D1 is SQLite-compatible — use any SQLite features (CTEs, window functions, JSON). Reads are globally distributed; writes go to the primary location. `DB.batch()` wraps multiple statements in a transaction. Free tier: 5M reads/day, 100K writes/day, 5GB storage.

